Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time from Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR after Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE for re-submission
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time it takes from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION in re-submission cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time for cases ending with Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR without further actions
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR occurs

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to the next activity in the process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in cases of re-submission
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time to resolve cases initially Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR but later approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time for Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR cases to be re-submitted and approved by any role
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE as a preparation for re-submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SAVED by EMPLOYEE'
